---- MODULE RoomLifecyclePlusCal ----
\* Room process lifecycle. Rooms are created on first join and terminate after idle timeout with no participants.
\* PlusCal version — generated by tlaiser
\* https://github.com/hyperpolymath/tlaiser

EXTENDS Naturals, Sequences, TLC

CONSTANTS Empty, Active, IdleTimeout

